AmiTEL. This software is (C) 1992-1997 Ldfa, any commercial use or sale without
written permission from the author is prohibited. You can copy and spread
freely this software according the following conditions:

   * the integrety of files must be preserved.

   * no file must be modified.

   * you don't ask for a more than nominal disk price and charge fee.

   * The download of this software is *only* allowed from BBS, FTP
